color red, 2L0Y_structure and chain A and resi 28
color red, 2L0Y_structure and chain A and resi 32
color red, 2L0Y_structure and chain A and resi 40
color red, 2L0Y_structure and chain A and resi 41
color red, 2L0Y_structure and chain A and resi 43
